VPC: 10.0.0.0/16        --> Contains
â””â”€â”€ Subnet: 10.0.0.0/24 --> Part of the VPC, smaller IP range
This is a common starting point when defining custom AWS networking â€” setting up isolated private environments for EC2, RDS, etc.

